Package honeyroasted.jype.system.resolution

Interface TypeResolver<T,K>

Type Parameters:
T - The type of objects that can be transformed into TypeConcretes
K - The type of objects that can be transformed into TypeDeclarations
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractTypeResolver, ReflectionTypeResolver, SequentialTypeResolver, TypeMirrorTypeResolver, TypeTokenTypeResolver
public interface TypeResolver<T,K>
This interface represents a type resolver capable of transforming some object into a Type. What method is used to resolve Types is left up to implementations.
